se quasars\nappear to prefer dense environments. Several possible reasons for this\ndiscrepancy are discussed, although further investigation is needed to obtain a\ndefinite explanation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2019 11:51:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-30"}
