\nbased approach is then used to rank the final Pareto optimal solutions and\nselect a single best design.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2019 15:28:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Jan 2020 17:57:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-06"}
