ple and also\ndepends on the mass of the particle. We also demonstrate that the result agrees\nwith that obatined using the operatorial approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2019 05:22:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-15"}
